{"tid":1580225,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"拯救藍絲！正式進入：「Facebook連儂牆計劃」","createTime":"2019-09-19T03:16:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T08:54:15.000Z","uid":48873,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8784389e129b4699e2809c0f723b53796ded58b9","tid":1580225,"uid":48873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T03:16:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />長話短說：成日話自己香港自己救, 請每人立即利用自己facebook做連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n做法：「每日都share反送中資訊」<br />\n目的： 打穿藍絲長輩同溫層！<br />\n</span><br />\n唔好話驚佢地見到會鬧，你facebook禁個share制先可以打破佢地嘅同溫層效應！比多d資訊去刺激佢地思考<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: blue;\">（係呀 佢地其實會諗野架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一個share，拯救一個生命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n長文：<br />\n<br />\n如果有日香港輸，一定係因為比班藍絲出賣。<br />\n如果我地要贏，一定要拎埋佢地嘅力量！<br />\n<br />\n天琦講過：「我時常提醒自己：政治的工作不只是要令支持自己的人繼續支持自己，而更是要令不支持自己的人轉為支持自己，改變想法，認同自己的方向。」<br />\n<br />\n我識身邊嘅人 <span style=\"color: gold;\">由黃轉藍好少，但藍轉淺黃</span>其實係易好多！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好睇少Facebook, 老一輩真係好鍾意分享同留言。我今日搭巴士望住個藍絲呀嬸係到睇幫港出聲 又會睇留言 另外又會打長篇大論去覆藍絲朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">藍絲媽媽最鍾意就係d煽情文章</span><br />\n例如「孩子！XXXXXX」<br />\n又或者「朋友！XXXXXX」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">藍絲叔叔最在乎就係錢同外國勢力</span><br />\n「反送中導致經濟/股市XXXXX」<br />\n「中美關係XXXXX」<br />\n<br />\n要打動佢地 變成淺黃，本人建議文宣小組係呢方面再努力d, 針對好Target audience. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">實行：做法其實好簡單，由facebook share做起。</span></span><br />\n(老一輩仲沉迷緊）<br />\n<br />\n1. 平時Like文宣pages, 新聞pages<br />\n例子： 文宣很清楚開花這個責任<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/105120017499651/posts/130618491616470?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F105120017499651%2Fposts%2F130618491616470%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5XIsb0SIwbGp5IKHDv9YBGc%3D&h=1b52c740\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/105120017499651/posts/130618491616470?sfns=mo</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<br />\n2. 見到認同嘅post, share+comment!!!<br />\n如果你有親人好藍&mdash;-&gt;可以唔加留言<br />\n如果親人淺藍&mdash;-&gt;加自己諗法 加強說服力 <br />\n<br />\n3. 高級間諜做法：入侵埋藍絲pages 留言逆轉風向<br />\np.s. 呢樣唔建議用自己ac<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n藍色媽媽們都已經做曬上面嘅野，仲分享勤力過你地呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  網絡連儂牆快d建成<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n緊急呼籲：<br />\n拯救身邊親人 幫佢地unlike垃圾page<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nshare&amp;comment 多d facebook 文宣post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫親友Like吓立場新聞同連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n假設：每個人都拯救到一個親友，我地戰力又double了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多你一個share 多好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aa3647353a763db507302e46d68d815d73a31a8","tid":1580225,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T03:17:03.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[公海 文宣 行動整合] 9.29全球抗赤納粹集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1579667\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1579667</a><br />\n全世界一齊對準ChiNazi極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BZiskWr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumb